# . Here we are feeding all the variables to the algorithm even though 6 out of 8 variables have less then 0.5 corrlation towards the target variable. # . Because we cannot conclude output based on two variables. # . There are missing values in the data,and the data is skewed. # . I have applied standard scaller and normalized the data # . we can improve the accuracy by treating missing values with median # . lets compare this with other classification algorithms # . Here the outcome variable is imbalanced instead of looking at accuracy rate it's better to take f1 score into consideration
